# Ship content changes to production

Cloudflare deploys from **git** (`npm install && node build.js` on push), not local `glyph/dist/`.

When you change page content, `glyph/scripts/generate-pages.js`, or `glyph/pages/**/*.json`:

1. Regenerate if needed: `cd glyph && npm run generate:force` (or `npm run ship` for full pipeline)
2. Validate + build: `node build.js --validate && node build.js`
3. **Commit and push without waiting for the user to ask** — include `pages/generated/*.json` and any script/template changes.

See `glyph/AGENTS.md` for the full workflow.
